OL,3,CAngela Rayner left in 'great concern'
OL,4,Cby death threats, court hears
OL,6,FMs Rayner, in a victim impact
OL,7,Fstatement that was read out at
OL,8,FLondon's Westminster Magistrates'
OL,9,FCourt, said: "I have not listened to
OL,10,Fthe recording, however I have been
OL,11,Fadvised by my office manager that the
OL,12,Fthreats were made with malice."
OL,14,FShe said she found this behaviour
OL,15,F"unacceptable" and felt "distressed
OL,16,Fand alarmed" by the threats.
OL,18,FMs Rayner added it "causes great
OL,19,Fstress and anxiety to all close to
OL,20,Fme", including her sons, who are under
OL,21,F18 years old, and her staff.
OL,26,@qD@NOUtD@_O]wD@AOUwD@NO]wD@YOUxD@LO]zD@
OL,26,ATOU|D@CO]
