OL,3,CAngela Rayner left in 'great concern'
OL,4,Cby death threats, court hears
OL,6,FElizabeth Harker, 63, of Luton,
OL,7,FBedfordshire, previously pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to sending a communication that
OL,9,Fwas "grossly offensive or of an
OL,10,Findecent, obscene or menacing
OL,11,Fcharacter" in the form of four
OL,12,Fvoicemails that targeted Ms Rayner.
OL,14,FProsecutor Olivia Grist told the
OL,15,Fcourt: "This defendant left four voice
OL,16,Fmails to a hotline ` all of which were
OL,17,Fabusive."
OL,26,@qD@EOUsD@JO]wD@HOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
