OL,3,CAngela Rayner left in 'great concern'
OL,4,Cby death threats, court hears
OL,6,FThe charge states she sent a letter
OL,7,F"which conveyed a message which was
OL,8,Findecent or grossly offensive for the
OL,9,Fpurpose of causing distress".
OL,11,FShe was caught on a Ring security
OL,12,Fdoorbell posting the offensive letter
OL,13,Fto the Luton home of Dorris Fortune on
OL,14,F2 November.
OL,16,FHarker was seen leaving the
OL,17,Fhandwritten note, containing "abusive
OL,18,Flanguage", at the door before running
OL,19,Faway, Ms Grist said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@\O]yD@^OUzD@IO]
