CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772532303
OL,3,CAngela Rayner left in 'great concern'
OL,4,Cby death threats, court hears
OL,6,FThe homeowner does not understand why
OL,7,Fthe the note ` which included slurs
OL,8,Fand comments such as "scroungers, I
OL,9,Freported you", "paedo" and "drop dead
OL,10,Fscrounge" ` was sent.
OL,12,FIn her victim impact statement, Ms
OL,13,FFortune said "whoever received this
OL,14,Fwould be very distressed as it is very
OL,15,Foffensive note".
OL,17,FShe said the note is "at the back of
OL,18,Fmy mind and has made me feel anxious
OL,19,Fat home even when I have the dog with
OL,20,Fme".
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@MO]qD@POUqD@VO]qD@\OUrD@IO]uD@
OL,26,ANOUwD@OO]yD@VOU|D@CO]
