OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772532303
OL,3,CAngela Rayner left in 'great concern'
OL,4,Cby death threats, court hears
OL,6,FMs Fortune said she did not understand
OL,7,Fthe thinking behind the letter,
OL,8,Fleading her to say "with a message
OL,9,Flike this, she appears angry and she
OL,10,Fcould even want to destroy the house".
OL,12,FHarker's defence lawyer Lewis Green
OL,13,Ftold the court: "She has a long-
OL,14,Festablished and entrenched history of
OL,15,Falcohol misuse of the last 30 years.
OL,17,F"She tell me she has been able to
OL,18,Fmoderate it.
OL,20,F"She tells me she is still drinking,
OL,21,Fthough not to the extent previously."
OL,26,@pD@TOUrD@eO]uD@QOUyD@AOU|D@AOU}D@eO]
