OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772532303
OL,3,CAngela Rayner left in 'great concern'
OL,4,Cby death threats, court hears
OL,6,FHarker was conditionally bailed and
OL,7,Fordered to undergo alcohol treatment
OL,8,Fassessment ahead of being sentenced on
OL,9,F24 March.
OL,11,FShe was also told that restraining
OL,12,Forders had been proposed by the
OL,13,Fprosecution as part of that sentencing
OL,14,Fhearing.
OL,16,FMs Rayner resigned as deputy prime
OL,17,Fminister and housing secretary in
OL,18,FSeptember after it emerged she did not
OL,19,Fpay enough stamp duty on an #800,000
OL,20,Fflat in Hove.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
